                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "T'accepte stupéfait comme on accepte un rêve.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Aldebaran ! Clarté de l'insondable grève,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Tu n'es pas seulement, dans les gouffres vermeils,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Un de ces inconnus que nous nommons soleils,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Tu n'as pas seulement, comme le kéroubime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "Une face splendide et sombre sur l'abîme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Ô spectre, ô vision, tu n'es pas seulement",
